# ===================================================================
# METIN2 CLIENT - FREETYPE FONT CONFIGURATION
# ===================================================================
# FreeType Font Configuration (Auto-Adjusted Version)
# ===================================================================
# Modern ImGui + FreeType integration with automatic parameter optimization
#
# USER CONTROLS:
#   - SIZE: Font size in pixels MANUAL 
#   - ENABLE_OUTLINE: 0 = off, 1 = on (MANUAL - simple on/off)
#
# AUTO-CALCULATED (you don't need to specify these):
#   - OVERSAMPLE_H/V: Auto-adjusted based on font size
#   - RASTERIZER_MULTIPLY: Auto-adjusted for optimal brightness
#   - OUTLINE_THICKNESS: Auto-calculated as ~5% of font size if enabled
#   - PIXEL_SNAP_H: Auto-enabled for small fonts (<12px)
#   - QUALITY: Auto-selected (LightHinting for small, HighQuality for medium, NoHinting for large)
#
# SIZE RANGES AND AUTO-ADJUSTMENTS:
#   Small fonts (<12px):   oversample=3x3, gamma=1.3, pixelSnap=ON,  quality=LightHinting
#   Medium fonts (12-24px): oversample=4x4, gamma=1.2, pixelSnap=OFF, quality=HighQuality
#   Large fonts (>24px):    oversample=2x2, gamma=1.0, pixelSnap=OFF, quality=NoHinting
# ===================================================================
#
#
# Example 1: Default UI font (14px) - balanced quality
FONT UI_DEF_FONT
PATH fonts/Tahoma.ttf
SIZE 14
ENABLE_OUTLINE 1
# Auto-calculated: oversample=4x4, gamma=1.2, outline thickness=1px, pixelSnap=OFF

# Example 2: Small UI font (11px) - optimized for readability
FONT UI_DEF_FONT_SMALL
PATH fonts/Tahoma.ttf
SIZE 11
ENABLE_OUTLINE 1
# Auto-calculated: oversample=3x3, gamma=1.3, outline thickness=1px, pixelSnap=ON

# Example 3: Large UI font (20px) - smooth and crisp
FONT UI_DEF_FONT_LARGE
PATH fonts/Tahoma.ttf
SIZE 20
ENABLE_OUTLINE 1
# Auto-calculated: oversample=4x4, gamma=1.2, outline thickness=1px, pixelSnap=OFF

# Example 4: Extra large title font (32px) - optimized for performance
FONT UI_DEF_FONT_TITLE
PATH fonts/Tahoma.ttf
SIZE 32
ENABLE_OUTLINE 0
# Auto-calculated: oversample=2x2, gamma=1.0, outline thickness=0px, pixelSnap=OFF